Name: GoFetch
About the game: Who's a good dog? YOU ARE! In GoFetch you get to be the dog and get the ball. Navigate through different terrain and mazes in a variety of unique maps, get the ball and bring it back! Multiple dogs can be unlocked, including: Beagle Border Collie Bull Dog Bull Terrier Chihuahua Doberman Pinscher German Shepherd Labrador Retriever Poodle Pug Rhodesian Ridgeback Saint Bernard Race to find the ball in lots of fun places like the park, the snow, inside a volcano or even in outter space! Why wait, get GoFetch today!
